ns are reproduced exactly using high-order CCM via\nthis \"brute-force\" approach; i.e., one in which none of the translational or\npoint-group symmetries of the finite lattice are used.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2010 19:37:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-02-24"}
