- Fisher relation for faint dwarf\nirregular galaxies, where it is often assumed that the gas is in a thin disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2010 06:03:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2010 18:20:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-04"}
